<nowiki>**</nowiki> Porsche is listed as parent company of مجموعة فولكس فاجن. This is only the case since January 2009, when Porsche acquired more than 50% of the shares of Volkswagen.

<nowiki>***</nowiki> شركة فورد is looking to sell Volvo.

<nowiki>****</nowiki> مجموعة هيونداي كيا للمركبات owns only a minority stake in كيا.

